===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|depthe|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{recons|diepþ|dīepþ|depth|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{recons|diupiþō||depth|lang=gem-pro}}, equivalent to {{suffix|deep|th}}. Cognate with {{etyl|fy|-}} {{term|djipte||depth|lang=fy}}, {{etyl|nl|-}} {{term|diepte||depth|lang=nl}}, {{etyl|gml|-}} {{term|depede|dēpede|depth|lang=gml}}, {{etyl|da|-}} {{term|dybde||depth|lang=da}}, {{etyl|is|-}} {{term|dýpt||depth|lang=is}}, {{etyl|got|-}} {{term|𐌳𐌹𐌿𐍀𐌹𐌸𐌰||depth|tr=diupiþa|lang=got}}.

